<paragraph id="400498C2CF41C1C9A96D351B21FE2999" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Zungen-Stendelwurz</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="E3F100DC4751EC9672DBBB3A9FD441D4" pageId="null" pageNumber="600" type="description">
<paragraph id="A173468EE23CDBF4B37F12B6A898883E" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="F2895DD1AC6CFD524E7A64DAD7AF892A" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Serapias" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="600" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vomeracea">
<emphasis id="401E8A89715AAD14151350C304C5B730" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">S. vomeracea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: 15-30 cm hoch; 
<emphasis id="D8E472E49812A824B66912A3D160516E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">
<normalizedToken id="2A17793198F9793960FD8866F9EEDBF9" originalValue="Tragblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Tragblaetter</normalizedToken>
die 
<normalizedToken id="0BB25E8FAF9D46EF184889373EAD70DA" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Blueten</normalizedToken>
nicht oder kaum 
<normalizedToken id="BD253A1B487C1C31FFE973AB2A04E838" originalValue="überragend" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">ueberragend</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="229CE278F002C0A9C546CC9153255660" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Blueten</normalizedToken>
kleiner
</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="EE4E01D935397B18DF8F46AAFD19A6E0" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
meist weniger als 20 mm lang); 
<emphasis id="A4722EEB07E2A3D6958B91D21B832BED" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">
Lippe am Grunde nur mit 1 
<normalizedToken id="D3DB8F4396F1C1ED979CDE4DD7C6D1B5" originalValue="Höcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Hoecker</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="7043BA3299AC097783DC1748AA5A456A" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="F6D1CD223ADF7635D94D75C6FD69C813" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="E86FE4D792DE6994B66F338617209582" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="30DC7943BA5EA7933EC1D399BB34BFF4" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">
<emphasis id="44B06BC4054BCA34A9F9ACAD8C8A2130" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1BACF1EFE222C770CEFD1F57B9138A40" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">
<emphasis id="B00FE94F2F83F1E673E828D1E337AB08" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Standort</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="56CC8ABD96FDF0A2CBA4D0F98D68435B" originalValue="ungenügend" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">ungenuegend</normalizedToken>
bekannt), wahrscheinlich wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="17D6E620A14386CC50DB488885B70F50" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Serapias" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="600" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vomeracea">
<emphasis id="28E609D4C549A8159D626AD7F09088FB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">S. vomeracea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D0693B00A9064326F442BC969ADE09CF" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">
<emphasis id="417E2E8C27D25F7DF40FEF542D4C0E3F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
In 
<taxonomicName id="7528C492779CA8664E3C67C6B3705E70" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Europa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="600" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Europa</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="A0286272F367430A6F83431CAAF2A70E" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="A82AA9E4A6E0D9C3BCA5DDDD78219D99" originalValue="Südfrankreich" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Suedfrankreich</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="E621F5B0B3EC1B1F6619ED11AE7423B4" originalValue="Alpensüdfuß" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Alpensuedfuss</normalizedToken>
, Istrien, 
<normalizedToken id="9707B6EC107B8754DC58D0BA14E8FD52" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Kreta; Nordwestafrika. - Im Gebiet: Val 
<normalizedToken id="976E87DCE8124B0A9DF4E4DAAF4295CA" originalValue="d’Ossola" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">d'Ossola</normalizedToken>
, Bergamasker Alpen (
<normalizedToken id="69808BE721C212AE6FA43C945EA4002B" originalValue="südlichste" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">suedlichste</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="10647E29289735CA0DE86115DCF6D75D" originalValue="Hügel" pageId="null" pageNumber="600">Huegel</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
